                        <head>No. 6<lb/><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                        <p>During the Ninth Session of the North Atlantic Council, which met in
                            Lisbon, February 20–25, discussion was held concerning the relationship
                            between the <gloss target="#t_OEEC1">OEEC</gloss> and <gloss target="#t_NATO1">NATO</gloss>. For documentation concerning the
                            Session, see <ref target="frus1952-54v05p1#pg_107">volume V, Part 1,
                                pages 107</ref> ff.</p>
                    </div>
